column1: Prerequiste- Terraform Training with AWS, Kubernetes and Cisco ACI

column2: Basic understanding of IP addressing, subnets, routing, DNS, and network protocols.
Basic understanding of Docker, containers, and containerization principles for the Kubernetes module.
Familiarity with cloud computing concepts and service models (IaaS, PaaS, SaaS).
Comfortable working with command-line interfaces in Windows, macOS, or Linux.
